  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with Colorectal Cancer(CRC);

          -  subjected to the Fast-Track processing of surgery;

          -  between 18 and 75 years old.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  American Society of Anesthesiologists(ASA) grade &gt; III;

          -  BMI &gt; 30;

          -  a history of abdominal surgery, endocrine or immune system dysfunction;

          -  recent blood transfusions, hormone or non-steroidal anti-inflammatory therapy during
             the past month;

          -  previous contraindication to epidural anesthesia.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
